flowchart LR
    PR[PR Created] --> Lint[Lint]
    Lint --> TC[Typecheck]
    TC --> UT[Unit Tests]
    UT --> Build[Build]

    Build --> SC{Sensitive change?}

    SC -->|No| Gate1[Standard gate]
    SC -->|Yes| SC2{Change type?}

    SC2 -->|Auth/Security| Force[Force HIGH-RISK]
    SC2 -->|Payment/Billing| Force
    SC2 -->|Schema/Migration| Force
    SC2 -->|Other sensitive| Classify[Content-aware classifier v4.33]

    Force --> RG[Release gate]
    Classify --> RG
    Gate1 --> RG

    RG --> REV{Reviewer evidence?}

    REV -->|Required, found| Pass[Gate PASS]
    REV -->|Required, missing| Block[Gate BLOCK]
    REV -->|Not required| Pass

    Pass --> Comment[PR Comment v4.39]
    Comment --> Merge[Ready to merge]
    Block --> Fix[Fix and re-push]
    Fix --> Lint
